snippet.title: CORR Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on the Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2330260/CORR/

Website:
https://gogogalagogames.com/

CORR is a DIFFICULT Souls-lite Boss Rush Action RPG where you Run-n-Gun & Hack-n-Slash your way through challenging boss encounters. To endure the strange, dark and whacky world of CORR, level up and customize your warrior build with berserk powers, tonics, talismans and more.
